    "(?i)(?:(?:asymmetric|mixed|divergent)\\s+(?:freshness|staleness|recency)\\s+(?:blend|composite|merge|presentation)|present\\s+(?:fresh|live)\\s+and\\s+(?:stale|old)\\s+as\\s+(?:single|one|unified)\\s+(?:state|verdict|score))"
  ],
